<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/hendry/2934652998/" title="iceweasel-noaddressbar"><img src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3034/2934652998_462143ea42_m.jpg" width="240" height="180" alt="iceweasel-noaddressbar" /></a>

<a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/hendry/903110103/" title="iceweasel-webcfullscreen"><img src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1351/903110103_3b82387709_m.jpg" width="240" height="180" alt="iceweasel-webcfullscreen" /></a>


* [[ISO]] and/or [[USB]] image varieties for [download](http://download.webconverger.com/)
* It is best to use Webconverger from an inexpensive [[USB]] stick, though you can install Webconverger to a hard drive
* Latest [Firefox Web browser](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Firefox) rebuild [Iceweasel](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Iceweasel) by default in every Webconverger.
* custom [[Artwork]] - your $HOMEPAGE/bg.png
* [[Kiosk_reset|blanking]] **timeout** with `kioskresetstation=<mins>`. Resets browser after user defined minutes of idleness/inactivity.
* [[Networking]] **wired** works simply with DHCP. [[Wireless]] works too!
* [[Adobe]] Flash & [PDF viewing](http://www.flickr.com/photos/hendry/3825411003/)
* [[Extensive_internationalization_support|i18n]] -  Exotic locales such as Chinese, Japanese and Korean (CJK) are supported. CJK keyboard switching via [scim](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SCIM) and many other types of keyboard setups, such as Swiss German. Spelling support with dictionaries in many languages.
* [[Printing]] support is included by default
* Different layouts of the browser, such as disabling address bar and [[digital_signage_modes|kiosk]]
* Screen [[blanking]] options and setting the resolution to a fixed sized (displays are autodetected by default)
* Locking down the bootloader so [[boot]] options cannot be altered by users on machine boot
